\centerline{\includegraphics[width=1.9\columnwidth]{suppl_figure1.pdf}}
\caption{\label{fig1}(color). Experimentally achieved scan images of a tightly focused linearly (y-polarized) Gaussian beam for the angular ranges shown in the back focal plane of the collection microscope objective (first row), and comparison with the scan images derived from the reconstructed focal field distribution (last row).}
